ComicInfo.Title: "It Was Still A Dark Time In The Kingdom..."
ComicInfo.Summary: LAST ISSUE! The loving, affectionate parody of one of the greatest science fiction franchises of all time comes to its hilarious conclusion! In the tradition of ROBOT CHICKEN: STAR WARS and SPACEBALLS, follow Lady Leica and Al Alone on the run from Lord Salvador’s bumbling men as Jean-Luc Groundwalker faces his most harrowing task yet: daddy issues! Will Lady Leica ever find competent cohorts? Will Al Alone ever get over his namesake? Will Jean-Luc stop asking so many darn questions? Find out here, in the last chapter of the fan-pleasing romp that skewers one of the greatest adventure stories ever!
